{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">了解稀盐酸和硅酸钠溶液的反应原理。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Na<sub>2</sub>SiO<sub>3</sub>+2HCl = H<sub>2</sub>SiO<sub>3</sub>（胶体）+2NaCl</span></span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：胶头滴管、试管；</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：硅酸钠溶液、盐酸、酚酞。</span></p>"},{"title":"仪器","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">在试管中加入3~5mL&nbsp;Na<sub>2</sub>SiO<sub>3</sub>溶液，滴入1~2滴酚酞溶液，再用胶头滴管逐滴加入稀盐酸，边加边振荡，至溶液红色变浅并接近消失时停止。静置，观察变化过程及现象。</span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">有白色胶体生成。</span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}